int on the shadow branch with the session's transcript and file changes\\n- Condenses the checkpoint to `entire/checkpoints/v1` and transitions the session to IDLE\\n- Offers to amend the last commit with the `Entire-Checkpoint` trailer (interactive prompt, or `--force` to skip)\\n\\n### Key decisions\\n\\n- **Transcript search across subdirectories**: Claude Code uses cwd (not repo root) for its project directory, so a session started from a subdirectory stores its transcript under a different project dir name. `attach` searches all project dirs that are subdirectories of the repo root as a fallback.\\n- **Agent-agnostic via `--agent` flag**: Defaults to `claude-code` but supports all registered agents (`gemini`, `opencode`, `cursor`, `copilot-cli`, `factoryai-droid`). The agent interface's `GetSessionDir` / `ResolveSessionFile` / `ReadTranscript` methods handle the per-agent differences.\\n- **No pre-state baseline**: Unlike hook-captured sessions that know the pre-session untracked files, `attach` has no pre-state. It uses `filterToUncommittedFiles` to limit checkpoint contents to files that are actually uncommitted, avoiding noise from already-committed changes.\\n- **Amend prompt with `--force`**: By default, shows the last commit and asks whether to amend it with the checkpoint trailer. `--force` skips the prompt and amends immediately. If the commit already has a trailer, it's a no-op.\\n- **Transcript helpers extracted to `transcript.go`**: `resolveTranscriptPath`, `searchTranscriptInSubdirs`, and related helpers are in a dedicated file to keep `attach.go` focused on the command logic.\\n\\n### Also included (merged from main)\\n\\n- **fix: `trail update` now pushes to remote** — `trail update` was only writing locally, unlike `trail create`\\n- **fix: GPG signing in test helpers** — tests creating bare repos now disable `commit.gpgsign` consistently\\n- **docs: Copilot CLI added to all documentation**\\n- **deps: bumped posthog-go, golang.org/x/mod, golang.org/x/term**\\n\\n## Test plan\\n\\n- [x] Unit tests for missing session ID, transcript not found, success path, duplicate session detection, and checkpoint ID output\\n- [ ] Manual test: `entire attach <real-session-id>` with Claude Code session\\n- [ ] Manual test: `entire attach --force <session-id>` amends commit without prompting\\n- [ ] Manual test: `entire attach --agent gemini <session-id>` with Gemini session\\n- [ ] Verify `entire rewind` works on attach-created checkpoints\\n\\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\\nMARKDOWN\\necho \\\"Copied to clipboard\\\"\",\"description\":\"Copy PR description to clipboard\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":727,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":43823,\"output_tokens\":1023,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":727,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYycusZcdvdZ5SUbZFJG8\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"5c84f23d-bea4-4ecd-8c2a-e2a0dc1cf1cd\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-12T17:58:54.651Z\",\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/ninawork/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"043d5e84-d945-425a-8479-8fccab0a38c3\",\"version\":\"2.1.74\",\"gitBranch\":\"attach-session-id\",\"slug\":\"floating-noodling-lemur\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"5c84f23d-bea4-4ecd-8c2a-e2a0dc1cf1cd\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"promptId\":\"bde541c6-dbcc-420f-9c8b-2cb382a299d8\",\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_01NBKhBNQNGzkvthY2eNDc4B\",\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"Copied to clipboard\",\"is_error\":false}]},\"uuid\":\"7fdbfd86-92b2-45a9-964f-6e6ede3d5092\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-12T17:59:10.680Z\",\"toolUseResult\":{\"stdout\":\"Copied to clipboard\",\"stderr\"